Package: ap2client
Section: embedded
Priority: standard
Homepage: https://github.com/dernasherbrezon/ap2client
Depends: hostapd, dnsmasq, fswatch
Architecture: armhf
Maintainer: Andrey Rodionov <dernasherbrezon@gmail.com>
Description: Switch RPi WiFi from access point mode to client mode
 Monitors wpa_supplicant.conf file for new networks. Once added, will try
 to connect to it. If success, then access point is disabled. If failure
 then switch back to access point.
